I will never allow
them to escape my mind.

00:40:26.080 --> 00:40:27.360
I have some bad thoughts.

00:40:27.360 --> 00:40:30.130
I'll get rid of them
as quickly as possible.

00:40:30.130 --> 00:40:32.980
I'll bring in new good
thoughts to my mind

00:40:32.980 --> 00:40:35.760
I'll never allow a new
bad thought to come in.

00:40:35.760 --> 00:40:37.880
That is called right different.

